{
  "stem": "1975.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 91.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because he used to send packages to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Were-- most of them were generated by, by, by me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he was very friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Plus the fact that he used to go hunting with the head of the-- with the chief of police from Berlin, from East Berlin.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I used to go with him, hunting birds and, and some other kind of animals, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I befriended the, the chief of police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I asked him-- and I told him that I-- from time to time, I wear also civilian, and the fact that I'm going to sometimes to the-- to the American sector, sometimes to the French sector.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in order for my protection, I need a, a German Ausweis, a German identification card.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In the beginning, he was a little bit mad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But then I said, look, I'm in the intelligence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And truthfully, what-- I mean, it's for my own protection and for the protection of my friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because the word was, you know, whenever we crossed the borderline between the sectors, we were at our own.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean, the commander always told me, I mean, if they catch you, I mean, we don't have any, any allegiance with you or anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, you are-- you are-- you're on your own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This was helpful for me later on when, when I planned my escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "This, this paper was almost the key to my-- to my escape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed in Berlin from 1945, the-- May 9th, till-- I stayed two years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was elevated to a-- to a lieutenant-- junior lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wanted me-- still, they wanted very badly I should become a-- join the Communist Party, which I said, I'm, I'm still not ready.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always tell them that I'm not ready.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
